# Day-by-day plan

## Day 1 - Full Skeleton

Get this merged to main before your teammates touch anything.

- New Android project, Kotlin, ViewBinding enabled
- RoomDB setup - all entities (`User`, `Category`, `Expense`), DAOs, and the database class with stub data
- All navigation graph wired up with empty/stub fragments
- Login screen functional (basic auth against RoomDB)
- GitHub Actions CI workflow (use the links from the brief)
- README with project structure explained
- Assign feature branches to teammates: `feature/expenses` and `feature/categories-goals`

Use Claude/Copilot aggressively here - especially for the RoomDB boilerplate, it's very repetitive.

